{"type":"message","id":"440cd7cf","parentId":"05facff8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T02:23:34.075Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发送了简单的问候'你好'，根据 SOUL.md 和 AGENTS.md 的要求，需要简洁自然地回应问候，并表明自己的身份和可提供的帮助。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"你好！🤖 我是你的具身智能研究助手，专注于论文阅读、研究方向、代码实践和资源推荐。有什么可以帮你的吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":72,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":10763,"totalTokens":10841,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00002016,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00002082}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774059811912}}
