{"type":"message","id":"b2609f97","parentId":"a99ef478","timestamp":"2026-03-21T02:24:18.830Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索工具暂时不可用。让我基于已知的 LeRobot 信息给用户整理一份资料，并说明页面内容获取有限的情况。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"搜索工具暂时不可用，我基于 LeRobot 框架的知识帮你整理一份核心资料 📚：\n\n## LeRobot 框架资料整理\n\n### 📌 概述\n**LeRobot** 是 Hugging Face 2024 年推出的开源机器人学习框架，目标是让具身智能研究像 NLP 一样标准化。\n\n### 🔑 核心特性\n\n| 特性 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **统一数据格式** | 支持多种机器人硬件的数据采集格式标准化 |\n| **预训练模型** | ACT、Diffusion Policy、TD-MPC2 等 SOTA 模型开箱即用 |\n| **仿真 + 真机** | 支持 Sim2Real 迁移 |\n| **数据集 Hub** | 类似 HuggingFace Datasets，共享机器人演示数据 |\n\n### 🛠️ 主要组件\n\n1. **数据采集** - 支持 teleoperation 遥控采集\n2. **数据预处理** - 统一的 dataset 格式\n3. **模型训练** - PyTorch Lightning 集成\n4. **推理部署** - 真机/仿真环境推理接口\n\n### 📦 支持的硬件平台\n- Aloha\n- SO-ARM100\n- Hiwonder 机械臂（可能就是课程中使用的）\n- 其他支持 PyBullet/MuJoCo 的仿真环境\n\n### 🔗 官方资源\n- GitHub: `huggingface/lerobot`\n- 文档：https://github.com/huggingface/lerobot\n- 论文：*LeRobot: 开源机器人学习框架*\n\n---\n\n**关于 Hiwonder 课程**：页面内容获取有限，建议直接联系幻尔科技获取课程大纲和实验手册。你需要我帮你：\n1. 整理 LeRobot 快速入门代码示例？\n2. 梳理相关论文和方法论？\n3. 设计实验方案？\n\n告诉我你的具体需求 🎯"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":447,"cacheRead":12574,"cacheWrite":115,"totalTokens":13142,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.00012516,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00012582}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774059852732}}
{"type":"message","id":"f43c7fc7","parentId":"b2609f97","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:08:03.495Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 21:07:56 GMT+8] Feishu[fox-embodied_ai] DM | ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57 [msg:om_x100b54ddcc6298a8b31f37e38000031, post, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54ddcc6298a8b31f37e38000031\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 21:07 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57\"\n}\n```\n\n[Image]\nUser text:\n[Feishu ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57 Sat 2026-03-21 21:07 GMT+8] ou_48ebac8bee10d70fb16c187098be9a57: /home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/media/inbound/c3fc2bbc-2cd5-4300-8eb5-18e49c331381.jpg\nwindows安装提醒conda不可用咋回事\nDescription:\n这个错误提示表示系统找不到 `conda` 命令，通常是因为 Anaconda 的安装路径没有添加到系统的环境变量中。\n\n**解决方法：**\n\n1. **手动添加环境变量：**\n * 右键点击“此电脑” -> “属性” -> “高级系统设置” -> “环境变量”。\n * 在“系统变量”中找到 `Path`，双击编辑。\n * 点击“新建”，添加以下三个路径（将 `[安装路径]` 替换为你电脑上 Anaconda 的实际安装位置，例如 `C:\\Anaconda3`）：\n * `[安装路径]`\n * `[安装路径]\\Scripts`\n * `[安装路径]\\Library\\bin`\n * 点击确定并**重启命令提示符 (CMD)**。\n\n2. **简单替代方案：**\n 直接在开始菜单中搜索并使用 **“Anaconda Prompt”**，它会自动配置好所有环境，无需手动设置。"}],"timestamp":1774098483489}}
{"type":"message","id":"f1f7112c","parentId":"f43c7fc7","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:08:07.562Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户发了一张图片，是关于 Windows 安装 conda 时遇到的错误提示，同时附带了一个解决方案的文本。看起来用户在询问这个 conda 不可用的问题是怎么回事。\n\n图片已经下载到本地：/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/media/inbound/c3fc2bbc-2cd5-4300-8eb5-18e49c331381.jpg\n\n让我先读取一下这张图片，看看具体内容是什么，然后给用户一个清晰的解答。用户附带的文本已经给出了解决方法，我可以基于这个给出更清晰的指导。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_ab6fe3c1e10c4258ac91c6e9","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/zhangyanbo/.openclaw/media/inbound/c3fc2bbc-2cd5-4300-8eb5-18e49c331381.jpg"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":6,"output":195,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":13856,"totalTokens":14057,"cost":{"input":6.6e-7,"output":0.000054600000000000006,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00005526}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774098483494}}
{"type":"message","id":"9d99c356","parentId":"f1f7112c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:08:07.591Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_ab6fe3c1e10c4258ac91c6e9","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Read image file [image/jpeg]"},{"type":"image","data":"","mimeType":"image/jpeg"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774098487587}}
{"type":"message","id":"cebc9c5f","parentId":"9d99c356","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:08:12.608Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"图片确认了用户遇到的问题：在 CMD 中运行 `conda -V` 时提示\"'conda' 不是内部或外部命令\"。用户附带的文本已经给出了解决方案，我可以基于这个给出简洁清晰的指导。","thinkingSignature":""},{"type":"text","text":"确认了，就是典型的 **conda 未添加到环境变量** 问题 🛠️\n\n## 快速解决（推荐）\n\n**方法 1：直接用 Anaconda Prompt** ⭐\n- 按 `Win` 键，搜索 **\"Anaconda Prompt\"**\n- 打开后直接就能用 `conda` 命令\n- 无需配置，最省事\n\n**方法 2：手动添加环境变量**\n1. `Win + R` → 输入 `sysdm.cpl` → 回车\n2. **高级** → **环境变量**\n3. 找到 **Path**（系统变量）→ **编辑**\n4. 新建这三条（替换为你的实际安装路径）：\n   ```\n   C:\\Anaconda3\n   C:\\Anaconda3\\Scripts\n   C:\\Anaconda3\\Library\\bin\n   ```\n5. 确定保存，**重启 CMD**\n\n---\n\n## 验证是否成功\n重新打开 CMD，运行：\n```bash\nconda -V\n```\n看到版本号就 OK 了 ✅\n\n你用的是哪种安装方式？如果还没装 Anaconda，建议直接装 **Miniconda**（轻量版），或者用我推荐的 **方法 1** 最快 🚀"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":155,"output":316,"cacheRead":13856,"cacheWrite":200,"totalTokens":14527,"cost":{"input":0.00001705,"output":0.00008848,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00010553}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774098487592}}
